Description: Screen recorder for creating animated GIFs
 GifCap is a Linux port of GifCam featuring a transparent capture
 window, in-app frame editing, and efficient GIF encoding.
 .
 Features:
  - Transparent recording window with click-through support
  - Smart frame comparison to reduce file size
  - Built-in frame editor with right-click operations
  - Hybrid X11 and Wayland support
  - Cursor capture with compositing
